org.opensaml.security.x509.tls.impl

Class ThreadLocalX509CredentialKeyManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opensaml.security.x509.tls.impl.ThreadLocalX509CredentialKeyManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyManager, X509KeyManager

    public class ThreadLocalX509CredentialKeyManager
extends Object
implements X509KeyManager
    An implementation of X509KeyManager which returns data based on the thread-local credential instance obtained via ThreadLocalX509CredentialContext.
